These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, egyptian, chinese, nigerian
1. the egyptian is in an odd position##4
2. the nigerian is between the mexican and the egyptian##2
3. the nigerian is on the right of the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | mexican | nigerian | egyptian | chinese |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, tomato, asparagus, lettuce
1. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
2. the person eating tomato is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating tomato is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | tomato | pineapple | lettuce | asparagus |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, documentary, romance, satire
1. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
2. the person watching horror movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching romance movies is between the person watching satire movies and the person watching documentary movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | satire | romance | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, ice-hockey, swimming, tennis
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
2. the person who's sport is swimming is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is tennis is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who's sport is swimming##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | water-polo | tennis | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, weightlifting, basketball, golf
1. the person who's sport is rowing is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | golf | rowing | basketball | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, polish, indonesian, pakistani
1. the polish is on the far right##1
2. the polish is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
3. the indonesian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | indonesian | russian | pakistani | polish |

