.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-14::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, skateboarding, ice-hockey, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
4. the person who's sport is water-polo is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | water-polo | climbing | skateboarding |

 #################################

 
